text: Ashby Mutumbami (born 15 November 1985) is a Zimbabwean cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Southerns cricket team in the 2006–07 Logan Cup on 3 May 2007. He is now an umpire and stood in matches in the 2016–17 Logan Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean cricketers Category:Zimbabwean cricket umpires Category:Masvingo cricketers Category:Southern Rocks cricketers Category:Southerns (Zimbabwe) cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Masvingo
